createText([[cn]],[[你在一个安静的营地中醒来，营地里有小木屋，位于阴森森的森林深处。树林里传来奇怪的声音，你知道那里有危险的东西。营地外面的某个地方有一个隐藏的实验室，有可怕的生物守卫着它。你需要在他们找到你之前找到逃生之门。快点，注意安全！]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[tw]],[[你在一个安静的营地中醒来，营地里有小木屋，位于阴森森的森林深处。树林里传来奇怪的声音，你知道那里有危险的东西。营地外面的某个地方有一个隐藏的实验室，有可怕的生物守卫着它。你需要在他们找到你之前找到逃生之门。快点，注意安全！]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[tha]],[[คุณตื่นขึ้นมาในแคมป์อันเงียบสงบพร้อมกระท่อมไม้ ลึกเข้าไปในป่าที่น่าขนลุก เสียงแปลกๆ ดังมาจากต้นไม้ และคุณก็รู้ว่ามีบางสิ่งอันตรายอยู่ข้างนอกนั่น ที่ไหนสักแห่งนอกค่ายคือห้องแล็บที่ซ่อนอยู่ซึ่งมีสิ่งมีชีวิตที่น่ากลัวคอยเฝ้าอยู่ คุณต้องค้นหาประตูเพื่อหลบหนีก่อนที่พวกเขาจะพบคุณ รีบและอยู่อย่างปลอดภัย!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[esn]],[[Te despiertas en un campamento tranquilo con cabañas de madera, en lo profundo de un bosque espeluznante. Ruidos extraños provienen de los árboles y sabes que hay algo peligroso ahí fuera. En algún lugar más allá del campamento hay un laboratorio oculto custodiado por criaturas aterradoras. Necesitas encontrar la puerta para escapar antes de que te encuentren. ¡Date prisa y mantente a salvo!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[ptb]],[[Você acorda em um acampamento tranquilo com cabanas de madeira, no meio de uma floresta assustadora. Ruídos estranhos vêm das árvores e você sabe que algo perigoso está por aí. Em algum lugar além do acampamento há um laboratório escondido com criaturas assustadoras que o protegem. Você precisa encontrar o portão para escapar antes que eles o encontrem. Apresse-se e fique seguro!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[fra]],[[Vous vous réveillez dans un camp tranquille avec des cabanes en bois, au cœur d'une forêt effrayante. Des bruits étranges proviennent des arbres et vous savez qu’il y a quelque chose de dangereux là-bas. Quelque part au-delà du camp se trouve un laboratoire caché gardé par des créatures effrayantes. Vous devez trouver la porte pour vous échapper avant qu'ils ne vous trouvent. Dépêchez-vous et restez en sécurité !]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[jpn]],[[あなたは不気味な森の奥深くにある木造小屋のある静かなキャンプで目覚めます。木々から奇妙な音が聞こえてきて、何か危険なものがそこにあることがわかります。キャンプの向こうのどこかに、恐ろしい生き物たちが守っている隠された研究室があります。彼らに見つかる前に、逃げるためのゲートを見つける必要があります。急いで、安全を確保してください！]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[ara]],[[تستيقظ في مخيم هادئ به كبائن خشبية، في أعماق غابة مخيفة. أصوات غريبة تأتي من الأشجار، وأنت تعلم أن هناك شيئًا خطيرًا هناك. في مكان ما خارج المخيم يوجد مختبر مخفي تحرسه مخلوقات مخيفة. عليك أن تجد البوابة للهروب قبل أن يجدوك. أسرع، وابقَ آمنًا!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[kor]],[[당신은 으스스한 숲 깊은 곳에 있는 나무 오두막이 있는 조용한 캠프에서 깨어납니다. 나무에서 이상한 소리가 들리고, 거기에 뭔가 위험한 것이 있다는 것을 알게 됩니다. 캠프 너머 어딘가에 무서운 생물들이 지키고 있는 숨겨진 실험실이 있습니다. 그들이 당신을 발견하기 전에 탈출하려면 문을 찾아야 합니다. 서둘러서 안전하게 지내세요!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[vie]],[[Bạn thức dậy trong một khu trại yên tĩnh với những căn nhà gỗ, nằm sâu trong một khu rừng ma quái. Những tiếng động lạ phát ra từ trên cây và bạn biết có điều gì đó nguy hiểm ở ngoài kia. Đâu đó ngoài trại là một phòng thí nghiệm bí mật với những sinh vật đáng sợ canh giữ nó. Bạn cần phải tìm được cánh cổng để trốn thoát trước khi chúng tìm thấy bạn. Hãy nhanh lên và giữ an toàn!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[rus]],[[Вы просыпаетесь в тихом лагере с деревянными домиками, глубоко в жутком лесу. От деревьев доносятся странные звуки, и вы понимаете, что там что-то опасное. Где-то за лагерем находится скрытая лаборатория, которую охраняют страшные существа. Вам нужно найти ворота, чтобы сбежать, прежде чем они вас найдут. Спешите и будьте в безопасности!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[tur]],[[Ürkütücü bir ormanın derinliklerinde, ahşap kulübelerin bulunduğu sessiz bir kampta uyanıyorsunuz. Ağaçlardan tuhaf sesler geliyor ve orada tehlikeli bir şeyin olduğunu biliyorsunuz. Kampın ötesinde bir yerde, onu koruyan korkunç yaratıkların olduğu gizli bir laboratuvar var. Onlar seni bulmadan kaçmak için kapıyı bulmalısın. Acele edin ve güvende kalın!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[ita]],[[Ti svegli in un accampamento tranquillo con cabine di legno, immerso in una foresta spettrale. Dagli alberi provengono strani rumori e sai che là fuori c'è qualcosa di pericoloso. Da qualche parte oltre il campo c'è un laboratorio nascosto sorvegliato da creature spaventose. Devi trovare il cancello per scappare prima che ti trovino. Affrettati e stai al sicuro!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[ger]],[[Sie wachen in einem ruhigen Lager mit Holzhütten tief in einem gruseligen Wald auf. Von den Bäumen kommen seltsame Geräusche und man weiß, dass da draußen etwas Gefährliches ist. Irgendwo hinter dem Lager befindet sich ein verstecktes Labor, das von gruseligen Kreaturen bewacht wird. Du musst das Tor finden, um zu entkommen, bevor sie dich finden. Beeilen Sie sich und bleiben Sie gesund!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[ind]],[[Anda terbangun di sebuah kamp yang tenang dengan kabin kayu, jauh di dalam hutan yang menyeramkan. Suara-suara aneh datang dari pepohonan, dan Anda tahu ada sesuatu yang berbahaya di luar sana. Di suatu tempat di luar kamp ada laboratorium tersembunyi dengan makhluk menakutkan yang menjaganya. Anda perlu menemukan gerbang untuk melarikan diri sebelum mereka menemukan Anda. Cepat, dan tetap aman!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);	createText([[msa]],[[Anda bangun di kem yang tenang dengan kabin kayu, jauh di dalam hutan yang menyeramkan. Bunyi pelik datang dari pokok, dan anda tahu ada sesuatu yang berbahaya di luar sana. Di suatu tempat di seberang kem terdapat makmal tersembunyi dengan makhluk menakutkan yang menjaganya. Anda perlu mencari pintu untuk melarikan diri sebelum mereka menemui anda. Cepat, dan kekal selamat!]],[[You wake up in a quiet camp with wooden cabins, deep in a spooky forest. Strange noises come from the trees, and you know something dangerous is out there. Somewhere beyond the camp is a hidden lab with scary creatures guarding it. You need to find the gate to escape before they find you. Hurry, and stay safe!]]);
